steps.name: Given Guest User should be on michaels home page
When User should enter the "Strathmore® 300 Series Canvas Pad" product in search bar
Then Click on search button to see the list of products
Then User should Click on the product "Strathmore® 300 Series Canvas Pad" from list
When User should select shipping method as a Store pickup from PDP page
When User should click on add to cart button
When User Should be click on view cart button
When User should enter the "yarn" product in search bar
Then Click on search button to see the list of products
When User should apply filter as MarketPlace under sales and offers
When User should Click on the product "Red Heart Soft Yarn" from list
When User should click on add to cart button

steps.name: When User Should be click on view cart button
When User should click on checkout button
When User will get model popup to click on continue as guest user
When User should provides shipping information like Valid First Name, Last Name,Addressline1 Addressline2,city,state,zipcode,email and Phone number
When User should able to select Payment Method as PLCC
When User should enter the Michaels Card Details like Name on Card, Card Number, Expiration Date, CVV
When User will check checkbox of Add A Gift Card
When User will Enter GiftCard Number, PIN and apply
When User will click on Place order button
When User will redirected to Order Confirmation Page
When User should find Order confirmation with order number
